pageContext.claim: “Big Tech doesn't want to report it. You ever see what they have trending? You know what they do? They take stories about me, if they can find anything bad, and then they make it worse. Trending, Donald Trump did this. Trending, the most boring stories, I mean, with all the things happening. With affairs, and this, and that they don't want to hear trending Donald Trump. It's, it's a whole big hoax. It's a big Tech hoax.”
pageContext.analysis: There's no evidence that the media or the social media companies such as Google or Facebook did anything to thwart Trump's chances at being elected -- or are trying to rig the upcoming election. Ever the conspiracy theorist, Trump constantly comes up with new ways "Big Tech" is trying to undermine him, even as he relies on social media to communicate with his supporters.
